===============================================================================
 EinsteinExact
===============================================================================
 Copyright 2011 Barry Wardell and Ian Hinder

EinsteinExact is an arrangement of Cactus thorns which provide exact solutions
of Einstein's equations.
===============================================================================


Getting the arrangement
-----------------------
The latest version of EinsteinExact will always be available from the project
git repository:

git clone --recursive git://github.com/barrywardell/EinsteinExact

Documentation
-------------
Documentation for the EinsteinExact pacakage is available in the \code{doc}
directory.

